\end_layout

\begin_layout Itemize
If the map has a face with 2 edges
\end_layout

\begin_deeper
\begin_layout Itemize
remove an edge of this face, and if the new map is 4 colorable, then the
 old map is also 4 colorable (see 
\begin_inset Quotes eld
